f=Product/loom/operational/commands/loom-commands.md · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\| Trigger phrases \| Skill \| Shortcut \| · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\|---\|---\|---\| · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\| "what are we assuming", "riskiest assumption", "leap of faith", "what could kill this" \| assumption-mapping \| /assume \| · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\| "run an experiment", "test this", "A/B", "fake door", "decision rule", "freeze criteria" \| experiment-discipline \| /experiment \| · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\| "have we tested this", "experiment history", "record the verdict", "did we try that" \| experiment-registry \| /registry \| · h1:loom — Command Triggers=\| "do we have PMF", "product-market fit", "Ellis survey", "retention curve", "double down or pivot" \| pmf-scorecard \| /pmf \| · h2:Precedence=proposed experiment queries experiment-registry FIRST re-running settled test needs stated delta. experiment-discipline run until metric (experiment-instrumentation) reports instruments verified-live. PMF verdicts route spec/marcus evidence double-down/pivot decision theirs, loom's. Criteria/decision-rule freeze precedes data always; post-hoc success bar bounces.